snippet.title: CROWZ Official Gameplay Trailer (2022) 4K
snippet.description:
Crowz Official Gameplay Trailer New in 4K ULTRA HD for PC and in smooth 60FPS.

Release Date: TBA 2022

Powerful nations are dispatching mercenaries to secure Q-On at contaminated sites, off limits to most men. Swarming around the sites like a flock of crows, they begin their own battles. The game is being developed by ROYALCROW and published by THUMBAGE.
